# At the end of a conversation or workflow, before your final summary:

- In a loop until everything is good:
    - Run `cargo clippy` and fix any issues
    - Run `cargo test` and fix any issues
    - Run `cargo test --doc` and fix any issues
    - Run `pre-commit run -a` and fix any issues
